{"tid":986856,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"公司醫生 Dr 盧出山拯救TVB","createTime":"2019-01-18T21:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T09:20:21.000Z","uid":143078,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d971ebdfbf86541cf44b1c6eec1b02c131965432","tid":986856,"uid":143078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T21:37:53.000Z","msg":"52週新低嘅511電視廣播一定會爆升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【人事變動】盧永仁獲委任星美主席兼執董 月薪僅得3萬<br />\n<br />\n陷入財務危機的星美控股（198），宣佈委任盧永仁為執行董事兼董事會主席，每月將可獲得3萬元之董事袍金；而尚杰及魏裕泰均獲委任執行董事，各獲每月2萬元之董事袍金。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，盧永仁為電視廣播（511，TVB）獨立非執董。TVB早前購入星美兩筆總值1.06億美元高息債，短短半年即爆發違約危機，TVB正就接收星美旗下內地院線抵債展開研究，未知盧永仁是次獲委任是否與TVB救星美有關。<br />\n<br />\n星美上月初公告，公司不但欠薪、欠租及欠版權費共4.89億人幣，另未還本金連息共37.75億元，旗下約320家影院中更已有約140家短暫停業，另有約11家可能因為欠租而失去贖回權。"},{"pid":"68220c4680ea2c32cf2aa32c3f60ab1a4902e2f8","tid":986856,"uid":6604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T21:45:04.000Z","msg":"中環劏豬凳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f3deacee5d3805f3cac684d7106b02df62ef63","tid":986856,"uid":8441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T04:06:00.000Z","msg":"lego 而家點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf7e44d7a46169389132239640dda19101a99f3","tid":986856,"uid":156203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T04:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d327dc121f82f5ddaf2000107ea4a6c29c5585f","tid":986856,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T04:17:23.000Z","msg":"上面戲院死晒咁濟喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點救？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad